g questions, alternatives, and personalities using images.","example":"https://h5p.org/personality-quiz","h5pMajorVersion":1,"h5pMinorVersion":0,"icon":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/personality%20quiz.svg","isRecommended":false,"keywords":["personality","quiz"],"license":{"id":"MIT","attributes":{"useCommercially":true,"modifiable":true,"distributable":true,"sublicensable":true,"canHoldLiable":false,"mustIncludeCopyright":true,"mustIncludeLicense":true}},"machineName":"H5P.PersonalityQuiz","majorVersion":1,"minorVersion":0,"owner":"Lumenia","patchVersion":8,"popularity":38,"screenshots":[{"url":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/styles/h5p-content-type-hub-screenshot/public/personality-quiz-01.png?itok=ygSGXtZF","alt":"Student's view - starting screen"},{"url":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/styles/h5p-content-type-hub-screenshot/public/personality-quiz-02.png?itok=79jwUFNT","alt":"Student's view - question 1"},{"url":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/styles/h5p-content-type-hub-screenshot/public/personality-quiz-03.png?itok=lDhEO4KA","alt":"Student's view - question 2"},{"url":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/styles/h5p-content-type-hub-screenshot/public/personality-quiz-04.png?itok=1zBGhax9","alt":"Student's view - question 3"},{"url":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/styles/h5p-content-type-hub-screenshot/public/personality-quiz-05.png?itok=rdoNJ4-j","alt":"Student's view - end screen"}],"summary":"Create personality quizzes","title":"Personality Quiz","tutorial":"","updatedAt":1607083118000,"canInstall":true,"installed":false,"isUpToDate":true,"localMajorVersion":0,"localMinorVersion":0,"localPatchVersion":0,"restricted":false},{"categories":["Other"],"createdAt":1488380236000,"description":"Gain feedback and ask open ended questions in Interactive Videos and other content types with Questionnaire. Questionnaire makes the user's answers available via an xAPI integration. This means that website owners may store the answers in many different ways. Answers may be stored in an LRS, the sites own custom storage or a script can fetch the e-mail address and use it to send the user an e-mail. On H5P.org answers are stored in Google Analytics.","example":"https://h5p.org/questionnaire","h5pMajorVersion":1,"h5pMinorVersion":0,"icon":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/questionaire.svg","isRecommended":false,"keywords":["questionnaire"],"license":{"id":"MIT","attributes":{"useCommercially":true,"modifiable":true,"distributable":true,"sublicensable":true,"canHoldLiable":false,"mustIncludeCopyright":true,"mustIncludeLicense":true}},"machineName":"H5P.Questionnaire","majorVersion":1,"minorVersion":3,"owner":"Joubel","patchVersion":3,"popularity":39,"screenshots":[{"url":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/styles/h5p-content-type-hub-screenshot/public/questionnaire-01.png?itok=zVNElQ9C","alt":"Student's view - question 1"},{"url":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/styles/h5p-content-type-hub-screenshot/public/questionnaire-02.png?itok=SdSQGHbW","alt":"Student's view - question 2"},{"url":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/styles/h5p-content-type-hub-screenshot/public/questionnaire-03.png?itok=sNnbfkv_","alt":"Student's view - question 3"},{"url":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/styles/h5p-content-type-hub-screenshot/public/questionnaire-04.png?itok=J8eZGmV0","alt":"Student's view - end screen"}],"summary":"Create a questionnaire to receive feedback","title":"Questionnaire","tutorial":"","updatedAt":1607083107000,"canInstall":true,"installed":true,"isUpToDate":true,"localMajorVersion":1,"localMinorVersion":3,"localPatchVersion":3,"restricted":false},{"categories":["Larger Resources"],"createdAt":1488380337000,"description":"Question Set is your typical quiz content type. It allows the learner to solve a sequence of various question types such as Multichoice, Drag and drop and Fill in the blanks in a Question set. As an author, there are many settings you can use to make it behave just the way you want it to. You may, for instance, customize the Question set with background images and define a pass percentage for the learner. The Question Set also allows you to add videos that are played at the end. One video for success, another if the learner fails the test. This might motivate learners to try again if they fail so that they get to see the success video.","example":"https://h5p.org/question-set","h5pMajorVersion":1,"h5pMinorVersion":19,"icon":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/question-set.svg","isRecommended":true,"keywords":["question set","collection","quiz"],"license":{"id":"MIT","attributes":{"useCommercially":true,"modifiable":true,"distributable":true,"sublicensable":true,"canHoldLiable":false,"mustIncludeCopyright":true,"mustIncludeLicense":true}},"machineName":"H5P.QuestionSet","majorVersion":1,"minorVersion":20,"owner":"Joubel","patchVersion":2,"popularity":3,"screenshots":[{"url":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/styles/h5p-content-type-hub-screenshot/public/question-set-01.png?itok=7xWQV7Vm","alt":"A multiple choice inside a question set"},{"url":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/styles/h5p-content-type-hub-screenshot/public/question-set-02_0.png?itok=ku46xHQX","alt":"A drag and drop inside a question set"},{"url":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/styles/h5p-content-type-hub-screenshot/public/question-set-03.png?itok=n1cnLs5j","alt":"A multiple choice inside a question set"},{"url":"https://h5p.org/sites/default/files/styles/h5p-content-type-hub-screenshot/public/question-set-04.png?itok=TrmmsdwT","alt":"The summary page"}],"summary":"Create a sequence of various question types","title":"Quiz (Question Set)","tutorial":"https://h5p.org/tutorial-question-set","updatedAt":1654168846000,"canInstall":true,"installed":true,"isUpToDate":false,"localMajorVersion":1,"localMinorVersion":17,"localPatchVersion":6,"restricted":false},{"categories":["Tasks"],"createdAt":1488380512000,"description":"Single choice set allows content designers to create que